The '''''Hasti''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttle]] serving the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was primarily used to insert [[Rebel elite commando/Legends|Alliance commandos]] into the battlefields. It deployed [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] during a [[Liberation of Gial Ackbar|battle]] with the [[Vehemence (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Vehemence'']].

